unning with &#8220;-mca btl_openib_verbose 1&#8221;, but didn&#8217;t see anything resembling a smoking gun. How should I go about determining the source of the problem? (This uses the same OpenMPI Version 1.8.1 / SLES11 SP3 / GCC 4.8.3 setup discussed previously.)<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Thanks,<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal>Greg<o:p></o:p></p><p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'><br><br><br><o:p></o:p></span></p><pre>_______________________________________________<o:p></o:p></pre><pre>users mailing list<o:p></o:p></pre><pre><a href="mailto:users@open-mpi.org">users@open-mpi.org</a><o:p></o:p></pre><pre>Subscription: <a href="http://www.open-mpi.org/mailman/listinfo.cgi/users">http://www.open-mpi.org/mailman/listinfo.cgi/users</a><o:p></o:p></pre><pre>Link to this post: <a href="http://www.open-mpi.org/community/lists/users/2014/06/24697.php">http://www.open-mpi.org/community/lists/users/2014/06/24697.php</a><o:p></o:p></pre></blockquote><p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman","serif"'><br><br><br><o:p></o:p></span></p><pre>-- <o:p></o:p></pre><pre>---------------------------------<o:p></o:p></pre><pre>Maxime Boissonneault<o:p></o:p></pre><pre>Analyste de calcul - Calcul Québec, Université Laval<o:p></o:p></pre><pre>Ph. D. en physique<o:p></o:p></pre></div></body></html>
